    "settingsVersion": 1,
    "info": [
        {
            "line": "Expedition HD Models is a port of the Anomaly Expedition 2.3 HD model to GAMMA D.U.X models "
        },
        {
            "line": "The Expedition HD models will integrate with the D.U.X. models such that: "
        },
        {
            "line": "- Most vanilla named NPC (vanilla stalker from bases, traders and important NPC) in every map are replaced with the HD models equivalent "
        },                
        {
            "line": "- All simulation spawns and non vanilla NPC (quests givers and any task faction squad spawn) should be a mix of D.U.X. models and HD models "
        },
        {
            "line": "This merge allows you to migrate your current gamma save and play with the new HD models and minimize any crashes due to quests and GAMMA compatibility as a whole "
        },
        {
            "line": "The HD models spawing mechanics can be very random, spawing at a base at a new game you won't necessarily see stalkers with new models but keep playing and they will show up "
        },
        {
            "line": "This porting is the same as in the profile GAMMA EXP Complete Edition and no crashes have been reported in a while "
        },
        {
            "line": "If you have a crash please report it to the profile thread "
        },
        {
            "line": "PAY ATTENTION: this profile only installs three mods in MO, you have to enable them in your modlist "
        },
        {
            "line": "The NPC Models from Expedition is a Gunslinger NPC and HD Models port built by Gerard11 "
        }                   
    ],
    "installationDiskspaceRequirementMB": "57473",
    "finalDiskspaceRequirementMB": "14337",
    "installCompletionMessage": [
        {
            "line": " 1. MEET THE REQUIREMENTS "
        },
        {
            "line": "       The mods installed by this profile only works with the latest GAMMA 0.9 "
        },
        {
            "line": "  "
        },                            
        {
            "line": " 2. LAUNCHING THE GAME FOR THE FIRST TIME "
        },
        {
            "line": "       enable the two mods installed by this profile "
        },
        {
            "line": "           - `Expedition HD Models - NPC`                                  contains all most model assets from Expedition modpack including the HD models "
        },
        {
            "line": "                                                                           if you don't mind overwriting any GAMMA model asset, put it at the end otherwise place it at the very top of your modlist; e.g before `23- THAP Rework - IENCE` "
        },            
        {
            "line": "           - `Expedition HD Models - Config`                               Toggle to enable/disable HD Models. You cannot disable HD models in a save that has NPC with HD models spawned "
        },
        {
            "line": "           - `Expedition HD Models - HDetoxyfier`                          Replaces on the fly (in game) HD models with vanilla models, it requires NPC Visual Replacer to be enabled "
        },                            
        {
            "line": "  "
        },                                  
        {
            "line": " 6. CREDITS "
        },
        {
            "line": "       Check the Expedition ModDb page's Credits section for credits "
        },
        {
            "line": "  "
        },
        {
            "line": "           https://www.moddb.com/mods/stalker-anomaly/addons/expedition-graphical-overhaul-addon-for-anomaly-151 "
        },
        {
            "line": "  "
        },
        {
            "line": "       HD models port "
        },
        {
            "line": "           The NPC Models from Expedition is a Gunslinger NPC and HD Models port built by Gerard11 "
        },
        {
            "line": "  "
        }
    ],
